<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0"/>
  <title>FAQs - Knowledge Hub</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/tailwindcss@2.2.19/dist/tailwind.min.css" rel="stylesheet" />
</head>
<body class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 via-white to-purple-50 min-h-screen px-4 py-12">
  <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto bg-white p-10 rounded-2xl shadow-lg">
    <h1 class="text-4xl font-bold text-center text-blue-700 mb-8">Frequently Asked Questions</h1>

    <div class="space-y-6">
      <div class="border-b pb-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-700 mb-2">❓ What is Knowledge Hub?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Knowledge Hub is a community platform where developers ask questions, share answers, and grow their coding skills together.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-b pb-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-700 mb-2">📚 Who can use this platform?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Anyone interested in programming! Whether you're a beginner or a professional, you're welcome to participate, learn, and contribute.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-b pb-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-700 mb-2">🌟 How do I earn badges or ratings?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          By actively participating—posting quality questions, answering others' queries, and receiving upvotes from the community.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-b pb-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-700 mb-2">🛡️ Is there moderation?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Yes. We have automated filters and a team of moderators to maintain a respectful and informative environment.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div class="border-b pb-4">
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-700 mb-2">📝 Can I edit or delete my posts?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Absolutely! Go to your profile and you’ll find options to edit or remove your questions and answers.
        </p>
      </div>

      <div>
        <h2 class="text-lg font-semibold text-purple-700 mb-2">📬 Need more help?</h2>
        <p class="text-gray-700">
          Reach out to our support team via the <a href="contact.html" class="text-blue-600 underline">Contact Page</a>.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
